bilingual.source: A Wiki challenge can be either interactive or non-interactive.
bilingual.target: Wiki质询可以是交互式的，也可以是非交互式的。
下面的图表是交互式的。

bilingual.source: The shopping cart is interactive and up to date.
bilingual.target: 购物车是交互式的和最新的。
交互式的特写做的尤其出色。

bilingual.source: Submerge yourself in the interactive Heineken Experience!
bilingual.target: 就让自己沉浸在这交互式的喜力啤酒厂体验之中吧！

bilingual.source: Remote, server side objects are designed for non-interactive use.
bilingual.target: 远程的服务器端对象可用于非交互式的场合。

bilingual.source: But with fiber-optic cables, television will become truly interactive.
bilingual.target: 但是，有了光纤电缆，电视就可以真正成为交互式的。

bilingual.source: But with fiber - optic cables, television will become truly interactive.
bilingual.target: 但是,有了光纤电缆, 电视就可以真正成为交互式的.

bilingual.source: The outcome of display is interactive, and it is changeable in angle and size.
bilingual.target: 显示的结果是交互式的，可以改变观测角度及任意缩放。

yingyinNormal.en: Tonight, we are playing the classic 1980 interactive text adventure, zork. It's the buggy beta version.
yingyinNormal.zh: 今夜，我们要玩经典的1980冒险游戏ZORK，而且是有漏洞的贝塔版。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
